rows.label: tev002111_MSG0010
rows.name:
I expect you to continue performing your
BLADE duties, like always. Once we've
nailed down the plan, I'll be in touch.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002111_MSG0020
rows.name:
It took long enough, but the plan's getting
into the final stages now. Try to get some
shut-eye before things get too...exciting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002111_MSG0030
rows.name:
There's still time before your deployment.
Take a breather while you canâ€”might be
your last chance for a while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002111_MSG0040
rows.name:
The escort'll keep the White Whale 2 in
the air. You BLADEs just stick to the plan:
take down Void and retrieve the cores![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002111_MSG0050
rows.name:
What're you doing back?! I was hailing
you the whole time, but I couldn't get
through. Glad to see you're alive, though.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002111_MSG0060
rows.name:
EM interference isn't affording us a whole
lot of visibility, so I won't be whispering
sweet nothings to you on this occasion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev002111_MSG0070
rows.name:
I'm sorry, but you're on your own.
The fate of humanity's riding on you.
...Make it count.[ST:wait ]
